text: Sam Groth and Chris Guccione were the defending champions, but did not participate. Gero Kretschmer and Alexander Satschko won the title, defeating Saketh Myneni and Divij Sharan in the final, 6–1, 3–6, [10–2]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Gemdale ATP Challenger China International Shenzhen - Doubles Category:Pingshan Open
